1. signup/signin cloudinary to get the api key/secret
2. create server endpoints to upload / remove files from cloudinary
3. resize the file in the frontend and send to the server
4. our server will upload the file on cloudinary and recieve the uploaded url 
5. those uploaded urls recieved by server will be sent back to the frontend 
6. it theis point the frontend will have the url of the uploaded image 
7. now we can save our product with images from cloudinary